{"tid":1738460,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"見大家想CUT無國界醫生CUT唔到, 我有份野可以FAX去","createTime":"2019-11-19T09:03:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T13:32:20.000Z","uid":218814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e302a248f25ec84f1b6667a024d6cfc6f705fa2e","tid":1738460,"uid":218814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:03:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/6z87re5u8s2tfwt/Cancellation%20Form.pdf?dl=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dropbox.com%2Fs%2F6z87re5u8s2tfwt%2FCancellation%2520Form.pdf%3Fdl%3D0&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqvTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=9c619add\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dropbox.com/s/6z87re5u8s2tfwt/Cancellation%20Form.pdf?dl=0</a><br />\n事源我之前九月想CUT 都係打唔通 EMAIL左佢地就SD左依份野<br />\nFAX 去就OK"},{"pid":"0d05689ce575b1bd904fc89ac2a8ccb915560375","tid":1738460,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X9ezQn6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX9ezQn6.jpg&h=eca97a61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9e8g3H6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9e8g3H6.jpg&h=8d0467fe&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n『取消每月捐款通知書』，填妥後電郵至&nbsp;donation@hongkong.msf.org&nbsp;亦可。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n取消每月捐款通知書PDF檔：<br />\n<a href=\"https://msf.hk/sites/hong-kong/files/Cancellation%20Form.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmsf.hk%2Fsites%2Fhong-kong%2Ffiles%2FCancellation%2520Form.pdf&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqvTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=5f8b1929\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://msf.hk/sites/hong-kong/files/Cancellation%20Form.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"48cabed9989ece880fb9643f7ccf025dc4583dd0","tid":1738460,"uid":322689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:32:20.000Z","msg":"無恥界醫生熱線已廢，想cut捐款但又打唔通hotline，可以直接打去銀行或者網上銀行自己cut，我以HSBC為例，做法係：<br />\n<br />\n1. 先登入HSBC網上理財（一定要電腦版，電話app不能）<br />\n2. 然後喺 &quot;我的銀行&quot; 欄目下揀 &quot;自動轉賬 &quot;<br />\n3. 揀 &quot;管理自動轉賬&quot;，然後就會見到你每月要轉賬嘅項目<br />\n4. 揀返 &quot;Medecins Sans F HK L&quot;，然後 &quot;刪除指示&quot; 再確認<br />\n<br />\n咁就可以成功cut捐款，但我唔知其他銀行網上理財係咪一樣，大家即管試吓！<br />\n<br />\n唔捐都唔夠，要攞返之前捐過嘅錢！方法如下：<br />\n可以打上card centre要求charge back返晒之前所有捐款<br />\nchargeback除咗攞返錢，商戶係要食好貴手續費<br />\n(chargeback 只限 credit card）"}]}